Class AccountBaseUser

  • java.lang.Object
    • AccountBaseUser
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Librarian, User

    public abstract class AccountBaseUser
extends java.lang.Object
    The AccountBaseUser abstract class is used to store attributes and abstract methods used within both of its subclasses: User and Librarian.
